    label "section_1426_subsection_b_item_3"
    class_name "item"
    text "(3) &#8220;available resources&#8221; means the plan's cash, marketable assets, contributions, withdrawal liability payments, and earnings, less reasonable administrative expenses and amounts owed for such plan year to the corporation under section 1431(b)(2) of this title; and"
