    class_name "item"
    text "(2) The clerk of the court shall transmit a copy of the review petition to the Secretary who shall file the record upon which the final order was entered as provided in section 2112 of title 28. Review petitions unless ordered by the court, shall not stay the Secretary's order. Petitions under this chapter shall be heard expeditiously, if possible within ten days of the filing of a reply brief."
  ]
