    class_name "item"
    text "(1) identify the employment goals and needs of the Nation, and assess the extent to which employment and training, vocational education, institutional training, vocational rehabilitation, economic opportunity programs, public assistance policies, employment-related tax policies, labor exchange policies, and other policies and programs under this chapter and related Acts represent a consistent, integrated, and coordinated approach to meeting such needs and achieving such goals;"
