  ]
  node [
    id 10796
    label "section_2201_subsection_a_item_2"
    class_name "item"
    text "(2) During the past decade, there have been major advances in modern technology. Technology is now a powerful force in the lives of all residents of the United States. Technology can provide important tools for making the performance of tasks quicker and easier."
  ]
  node [
    id 10797
    label "section_2201_subsection_a_item_3"
    class_name "item"
    text "(3) For some individuals with disabilities, assistive technology devices and assistive technology services are necessary to enable the individuals&#8212;"
  ]
  node [
    id 10798
    label "section_2201_subsection_a_item_3_subitem_A"
    class_name "subitem"
    text "(A) to have greater control over their lives;"
  ]
  node [
    id 10799
    label "section_2201_subsection_a_item_3_subitem_B"
    class_name "subitem"
    text "(B) to participate in, and contribute more fully to, activities in their home, school, and work environments, and in their communities;"
  ]
  node [
