    label "section_2704_subsection_c_item_1"
    class_name "item"
    text "(1) the provision of technical assistance to workers, worker organizations, employers, State economic development agencies, State industrial extension programs, Advanced Technology Centers, and National Manufacturing Technology Centers to identify advanced workplace practices and strategies that enhance the effective evaluation, selection, and implementation of advanced workplace technologies;"
  ]
  node [
    id 11957
    label "section_2704_subsection_c_item_2"
    class_name "item"
    text "(2) the researching and identification of new and advanced workplace technologies, and advanced workplace practices that promote the improvement of workers&#8217; skills, wages, working conditions, and job security, that research the link between advanced workplace practices and long-term corporate performance, and which are consistent with the needs of local communities and the need for a healthy environment; and"
  ]
  node [
